cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV

The paper deals with training collaborative filtering models using deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves optimizing ranking-based metrics, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks for scoring and ranking also relates to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV).
